1.10	Foundation_of_Tertiary_Institutions_of_the_Northern_Metropolis	Foundation of Tertiary Institutions of the Northern Metropolis	Foundation of Tertiary Institutions of the Northern Metropolis, FOTIM, is the biggest academic association in South Africa. FOTIM consists of nine universities and universities of technology in the Gauteng, Limpopo Province and North West Province.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5e/Foundation_of_Tertiary_Institutions_of_the_Northern_Metropolis.jpg/200px-Foundation_of_Tertiary_Institutions_of_the_Northern_Metropolis.jpg
